{quote}
Make sense, but I'd like to differentiate the two cases, and log warning messages. How about the following logic?
{code}
if (individual <= 0) {
  max = global;
  LOG.warn("invalid");
} else if (individual >= global) {
  max = global;
  LOG.warn("larger than global");
} else {
  max = individual;
}
{code}

